name: [Sign-in User][.com] Reordering from order history page by clicking on "Buy All Again" Button

steps.name: Given User will open website
When User accept cookies
When the user provides valid credentials to sign in
Then User should click in sigin button
When User will click on cart button
Then User Will Clear the Cart
When user navigates to the "Account Dashboard" via the user profile menu
Then the Michaels Rewards details should be visible
Then Account Dashboard Page should be displayed
When User click on Orders and purchase option from My Account section
Then Order History sub option should be displayed under Order and purchase
When User click on Order History from Order and purchase section
Then Verify Order History Page should be displayed

When User will add the Card Details like Name on Card,Card Number,Expiration Date,CVV

When User should find Order confirmation with order number
